两款Adobe插件AutoOCR和TextExtraction

AutoOCR  -  自动设置好参数，对PDF进行OCR处理，默认设置是[所有页面][CHS:中文
(简体)]
[ClearScan][600dpi]
TextExtraction  -  将OCR后的文本输出到c:\outputfiles目录里，包括txt和doc文
件。

这2个插件适合于批量处理PDF文件,调用方式很简单(不同语言会略有差别)：
App.MenuItemExecute("ADBE:AutoOCR")
App.MenuItemExecute("ADBE:TextExtraction")


---------------------------------------------------------------------

English Description:

Adobe-plugins including AutoOCR and TextExtraction

AutoOCR  -  auto setting parameter,[All pages][Primary OCR Language:Chinese(Simplified)][ClearScan][600dpi].

TextExtraction  - save pdf as txt and doc,output to c:\outputfiles directory.

This two plug-in suitable for batch processing PDF files, calling very simple way (in different languages ​​will be slightly different):
App.MenuItemExecute("ADBE:AutoOCR")
App.MenuItemExecute("ADBE:TextExtraction")




